==English==

===Etymology===
Old English [[ridan|rīdan]], from Germanic ''*ridanan'', from Indo-European ''*reidh-''. Cognate with Dutch [[rijden]], German [[reiten]], Swedish [[rida]]; and (''from Indo-European'') with Welsh [[rhwyddhau]] ‘hurry’.

